  `pow(base, exp, mod)`  [, mod]  base exp  mod    .     , base exp   exp   . <mark>`pow(base, exp, mod)`   `pow(base, exp) % mod`    .</mark>

  {% code lang:python %}
    >>> print(pow(10, 2, 3))  # 10^2 % 3
