### The Minion Game

{% note info %}
 :  S   (Stuart, Kevin)  (consonant), (vowel)             
 : 'BANANA' 'ANA' 2   score 2 .   
![minion game](https://s3.amazonaws.com/hr-challenge-images/9693/1450330231-04db904008-banana.png)
{% endnote %}

{% tabs example2 %}
  <!-- tab INPUT @code -->
  BANANA
  <!-- endtab -->

